ff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">二、用户的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">白条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">账户、密码和（或）数字证书是</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">识别</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">用户身份及指令的唯一标志，所有使用用户账户、密码和（或）数字证书的操作即为用户的（授权）操作行为，任何使用用户的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">白条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">账户、密码和（或）数字证书发送</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">至</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">及</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">委托</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">的第三方公司的使用</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">信用付款服务</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">或</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">支付</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">或其他相关指令构成用户不可撤销的授权指示，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">或</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">委托</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">的第三方公司对于依照该指示进行的操作行为及其结果不承担任何责任。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">用户接受本协议即表明了解和</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">确认</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">制定</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的关于使用信用付款服务的所有规定，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">接受</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">制订的全部收费项目和条件，以及</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">公布</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的任何与延后付款或分期付款有关的条款约束并遵守本协议及其之后修订版本。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第一条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">术语定义</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">除非本协议正文另有明确所指，在本协议中所用下列术语定义如下：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（一）平台规则：指标示在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">或</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">合作</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">商户之上的，与用户</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">使用</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站所提供的平台服务、信用付款服务有关的任何规范性文件，包括但不限于购物流程、售后政策、退款说明、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">服务费用计算规则等，同时</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">包括</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">就信用付款服务制定的特别规则，以下统称</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">平台规则</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（二）信用付款服务：指</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">为</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">符合条件的用户在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">及</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">合作</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">商户购买商品或服务提供的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">先购物、后付款</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的信用付款方式的服务。</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">信用付款方式</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">指用户在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">合作</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">商户上消费时，可依据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">服务</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">规则及相应申请流程，享受</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">由</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">提供</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的相应的延后付款或分期付款的付款方式。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（三）</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">：是信用付款服务的营销推广名称，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">可</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">根据法规和营销推广的实际情况对该名称进行调整。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（四）信用付款额度：指</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">根据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">用户在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">历史购买商品的支付信用记录和消费状况等因素综合评估确定的最高信用付款额度，用户可依据实时公布的平台规则以及相应要求激活、查询和使用该额度。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（五）消费：指用户在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">合作</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">商户购买商品或者接受服务并支付款项的行为。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（六）适用商户：指用户可以使用信用付款服务购买的商户范围，适用商户会根据相关法律法规、本协议约定和</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">情况随时调整。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（七）消费本金：指用户在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">及</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">合作</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">商户每一笔消费需要支付的该消费对应价款的金额。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（八）消费记账日：指用户选择使用信用付款服务对当笔消费进行付款的起始日期。消费记账日以</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">支付结算系统确定的日期为准，用户可以在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">我的待还款</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">中查阅。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（九）到期付款日：指用户应付款的最晚日期。在延后付款方式下，到期付款日是用户承诺的最晚付款日期，在分期付款方式下，到期付款日为每一期款项应支付的最晚日期。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十）延后付款：指用户在使用信用付款服务时确定的一个日期，用户承诺在该日期之前支付全部消费本金的一种付款方式。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十一）延后付款期：指用户选择延后付款时，从消费记账日起至到期付款日之间的实际天数，根据用户的资信状况综合评估核定，最长不超过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">30</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">天。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十二）分期付款：指用户确定将消费本金分为若干期付款，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">按照</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">规定收取费用的一种付款方式。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十三）分期付款期数：指用户选择分期付款分摊支付的月数，最长不超过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">24</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">个月。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十四）分期服务费：指用户选择分期付款时须承担的分期付款服务费用，分期服务费率以《</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条服务费用计算规则》展示的内容为准，每期服务费与当期本金一同收取。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十五）到期应付款：指用户在到期付款日前应支付的全部金额，包括但不限于消费本金、分期服务费、违约金等。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十六）违约金：指用户未按本协议约定在到期付款日前支付全部应付款而导致信用违约时，根据本协议的违约金计算方式及《</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条服务费用计算规则》的内容，向</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">支付</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的相关违</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">约金额。违约金具体比例以</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">金融帮助</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">中心页面公布的《</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条服务费用计算规则》展示的内容为准。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十七）</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网银在线</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">账户：</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">指网银</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">在线公司向用户提供的第三方支付服务。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十八）用户个人信息：指用户在申请开通及使用信用付款服务时依据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">要求所提供的个人身份信息及历史消费情况，包括但不限于姓名、证件号、银行卡账号、联系地址、手机号码等。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（十九）关联公司：本协议所称</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">关联公司</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">是指由一方直接控制或间接控制；或直接或间接控制一方；或与一方共同控制同一家公司或能对其施加重大影响；或与一方受同一家公司直接或间接控制的公司。包括但不限于一方的母公司、子公司；与一方受同一母公司控制的子公司；一方的合营企业、联营企业等。这里的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">公司</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">指任何一人公司、有限责任公司或股份有限公司；</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">控制</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">是指直接或间接地拥有影响所提及公司管理的能力，无论是通过所有权、有投票权的股份、合同或其他被人民法院认定的方式。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第二条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">信用付款服务的申请</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、根据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">服务</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">规则及相应流程完成用户信息提交、用户信息验证并通过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">审核</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、完成相应的实名认证、快捷支付绑定等相应操作。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、满足本条约定的用户在仔细阅读本协议内容，同意给予本协议中以加粗字体约定的相应授权并点击接受本协议全部内容后，开通信用付款（</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">）服务。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第三条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">付款方式、服务费用收取及结算</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（一）付款方式：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、用户可在信用付款服务适用范围、可用额度范围内进行消费。使用信用付款服务时可在消费记账</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">日选择</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">延后付款或分期付款等两种付款方式，并在到期付款日完成到期应付款的支付。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、用户选择延后付款的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">,</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">可享受延后付款服务，即</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">自消费</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">记账日起至到期付款日止的期间内（最长不超过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">30</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">天）不需支付任何服务费用。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、用户选择分期付款的，可将消费本金按</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">月分</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">摊支付（最长不超过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">24</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">个月），并须承担相应的分期付款服务费用，每期服务费与当期本金一同收取。服务费金额：每期分期服务费</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">=</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">消费本金</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">×</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">分期服务费率（月），服务费率以《</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条服务费用计算规则》公示的内容为准。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、用户产生信用违约情形时，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权向用户按日收取违约金，具体计算公式为：违约金（日）</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">=</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">应付未付总额（本金</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">+</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">分期服务费）</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">×</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">违约金比例，违约金（日）不足</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">0.01</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">元时按</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">0.01</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">元收取；总违约金</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">=</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">违约金（日）</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">×</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">违约天数。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">用户支付应付款金额时，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">将</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">按照违约金（如有）、分期服务费（如有）、消费本金的顺序进行冲抵。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（二）服务费用收取及结算：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、结算方式：用户对应付款项（包括但不限于本金、分期服务费、违约金等）进行付款结算时可在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">金</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">融</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">APP</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">商城</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">APP</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">微信公众号</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">等进行操作，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">根据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条的实际运营情况，委托</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">关联</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">公司收取相关款项</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、结算凭证：用户选择延后付款及分期付款时，用户与</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">结算</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的依据是</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">查询</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">系统的查询结果以及银行对账凭证，后者没有记录而前者有记录的，以前者的查询结果为准；两者存在差异的，以银行对账凭证为准。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（三）用户使用本协议约定的信用付款服务进行消费下单成功后，由于各种原因导致用户进行</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">取消订单</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">或</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">“</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">申请退货</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">”</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">操作，此种情形下，用户已支付的分期服务费、违约金等款项，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">不再</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">退还。退货金额的确定以及其他退货相关事宜以</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">以及</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">合作</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">商家的商品售后服务政策及其他相关退货规定为准。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（四）如用户的信用付款服务被暂停、或用户申请提前终止服务，则该用户的所有应付款项视为全部到期并应由用户全部予以支付。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（五）提前还款：用户选择分期付款并在支付完首期应付款后要求提前还款的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">,</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">需经过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">确认；针对提前还款情形，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">不</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">另外加收用户额外的提前还款服务费</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">,</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">也</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">不</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">返还用户已经支付的分期付款服务费用，同时用户应将剩余的分期服务费全部一次性还清。用户申请提前还款的具体流程以平台规则约定为准。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第四条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">违约行为及违约处理</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">（一）违约行为</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">用户发生下列任</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">一</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">情形，均构成违约：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、未按本协议规定按时足额支付应付款。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、向</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">提供</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">过期、虚假等不真实个人的信息、或相关个人信息被</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">认定</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">为可疑、过期或虚假信息。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、出租、转借或以其他方式将使用信用付款服务过程中的相关账户、密码、数字证书、身份证信息、手机号码、银行卡信息、住址、邮箱等信息交由用户之外任何</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">其他第三</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">方使用的。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">4</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、以非法套现、非法获取不正当利益为目的，通过非法、不正当操作或与非法商户、非法中介组织、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">其他第三</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">方等串通合作，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">违反</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">信用付款服务平台规则及各项管理规定、被</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">通过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">风险监测、风险管理方式进行识别、或</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">以</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">其他合法合</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">规</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">方式获取用户以本条方式进行非法套现情形的。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">5</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、用户的资信情况出现其他重大不利变化导致用户无法继续按时足额支付应付款的情形。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">6</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、用户被宣告失踪、宣告死亡、处于限制民事行为能力或丧失民事行为能力状态、被刑事监禁、或用户发生重大疾病、重大事故等可能影响付款能力的情况而没有及时</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">通知</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、并继续使用信用付款服务的。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">7</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、用户违反本协议约定的其他情形或被</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">认定</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">用户存在违约行为的其他情形。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">（二）违约救济</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如用户出现上述违约情形，或违背本协议项下其他任何义务、陈述、保证或承诺的，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权采取下列一项或多项措施，包括但不限于：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、调整或取消用户的信用付款信用额度。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、对用户的信用付款交易采取订单拦截、用户资料、用户信息核实、要求用户提供相关材料等方式。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、要求用户纠正违约行为并向</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">提供</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">相关信息材料。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">4</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、有权宣布本协议项下未支付的应付款项提前到期，并要求用户提前支付全部应付款项；并提前支付相关分期服务费、违约金等费用。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">5</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、以合法手段追偿应付款项（包括但不限于委托债务催讨公司、律师事务所等</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">其他第三</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">方机构代为追讨，申请相关部门进行调查、向法院提起诉讼等），由此引起的一切费用由用户承担。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">6</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、在媒体（包括而不限于电视、报纸、网站等公开媒体和</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、客户端、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">微信公众号</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">等）上公布用户的个人基本信息、债务信息、信用信息等内容。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">7</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、根据法律法规或本协议约定有权采取的其他违约救济措施。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">用户在此同意，在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">进行</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">违约救济时，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权直接从用户与账户绑定的银行卡中直接扣减使用信用付款服务应支付的全部款项（含服务费、违约金、调查费、律师费等所有费用）；</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权采取其他相关救济措施进行追讨，包括使用或授权第三方查询、索取、留存和使用用户的资信状况、财务状况、其他与评定用户信用付款额度及付款能力有关的个人信息等方式进行违约救济；</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权使用或授权第三方使用用户个人信息对违约欠款进行追偿。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第五条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权利和义务</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（一）用户的权利和义务：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、有权要求</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">对</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">用户提供的有关信息予以保密，但法律法规另有规定、用户予以授权、或本协议另有约定的除外。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">享有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">对信用付款服务所承诺的各项服务，有权监督服务质量，并对不符合质量的服务进行投诉。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、有权知悉信用付款服务的功能、使用方法，收费项目、收费标准、适用费率及相关的计算规则。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、向</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">提供</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">真实、有效的资料。如迁往异地、工作变动、通讯地址及电话变更、单位名称变更、电子邮箱或身份证件号码变更等，应及时</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">通知</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">，包括但不限于登陆账户修改、书面通知、在线或电话联系客服等。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">5</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、仔细阅读并充分理解本协议、重要提示及其他所有相关资料和文件，并持续</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">关注</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">通过网站等方式向用户公示的协议修订，以及对上述资料和文件的修改和变更。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">6</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、用户应妥善保管本人的账户名、密码、绑定的手机号码、手机校验码等与</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">关的一切信息。用户应确保不向其他任何人泄露账户信息和密码。对于因密码泄露所致的损失，由用户自行承担。如用户发现有他人冒用或盗用本人账户及密码或任何其他未经合法授权之情形时，应立</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">即以有效方式</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">通知</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">，要求其暂停相关服务。同时，用户</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">理解</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">对相应的请求采取行动需要合理期限，在此之前，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">对</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">已执行的指令及（或）所导致的用户损失不承担任何责任。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">7</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">用户不得以出租、转借或以其他方式将使用信用付款服务过程中的相关账户、密码、数字证书、身份证信息、手机号码、银行卡信息、住址、邮箱等信息交由任何</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">其他第三</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">方使用，否则由此导致的损失及相关后果由用户承担。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">8</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、用户不得以非法套现、非法获取不正当利益为目的，通过非法、不正当操作或与非法商户、非法中介组织、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">其他第三</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">方等串通合作，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">违反</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">信用付款服务平台规则及各项管理规定，否则由此导致的损失及相关后果由用户承担。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">9</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、用户应按时支付信用付款服务项下的应付款项（包括但不限于本金、分期服务费、违约金等），不得以商品纠纷为由拒绝支付信用付款服务项下的应付款项。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">10</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、按照</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">制订</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">并公布的收费标准支付服务费及其他费用。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">11</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、用户声明在接受本协议时本人不存在任何违反法律、法规与规章的行为或情形；若用户的上述声明虚假或者上述承诺未</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">被履</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">行，或者用户可能发生违法违规风险，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权提前终止</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">本服务</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">或采取本协议约定或法律允许的其他救济措施。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（二）</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权利和义务：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、对不遵守有关法律法规、本协议等规定的用户（包括但不限于用户未在规定期限内支付应付款项的）或者</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">理由认为用户不再符合信用付款方式付款的使用条件时，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权基于合理怀疑拒绝用户继续使用信用付款方式进行付款，并</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">由</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站将本条第</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">项中规定方式提醒客户，如客户在合理期限内未向</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">公司</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">提供充分证据以消除该等合理怀疑的，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权提前暂停信用付款服务而不必事先通知用户本人。用户对</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">停止其信用付款服务的使用有异议的，需要按照</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">要求，依据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">所提供的客户服务等方式向</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">公司</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">提供充分证据以消除该等合理怀疑，具体异议提出方式及解决方式以平台规则约定为准。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、为有针对性地向用户提供新的服务、机会以及优惠信息等，用户了解并同意</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">依据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">用户在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">已经认可的促销信息推送方式（包括但不限于电子邮件、站内消息和手机短信等）向用户通知这些信息。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有权通过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">信函、短信、电子邮件、电话、上门或司法途径等方式向用户催收应付款项。用户同意</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权授权第三方通过手机短信、站内信、电话提醒、上门外访和寄送信函等方式，督促用户按时支付所有应付款项，包括但不限于消费本金、分期服务费、违约金等，其中手机短信、站内信、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">微信在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">发出时即视为送达。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">保留</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">对用户收取费用的权利，且有权在有关法律法规允许的范围内，结合信用付款和业务发展等实际情况，维护和更新信用付款服务的适用范围、各项使用功能、服务范围和收费标准，并通过网站公告等方式及时通知用户。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">5</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权根据相关适用法律，将在信用付款服务关系建立和存续期间获得的用户的个人基本信息、债务信息、信用信息（即适用法律规定的对乙方信用状况的客观状态）等有关信息提供给相关政府管理部门、行业监督管理机构或其他合法设立的征信管理机构等。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">6</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">义务接受用户对于信用付款方式付款相关信息的查询服务，将向用户通过</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（公告方式）、电子邮件、手机短信等向用户公示信用付款产品和服务、重要提示、服务协议、计费标准等信息。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">7</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建立针对信用付款服务的公平、有效的投诉制度的义务，并公开投诉程序和投诉电话。对用户关于账务情况的查询和改正要求给予答复。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">8</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">将</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">根据行业规则、国家相关法律法规及业务发展情况为用户提供相关的优惠活动或服务，活动或服务规则以届时</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">相关</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">页面公布的内容为准。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">9</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">对</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">用户的个人基本信息、债务信息、信用信息有权予以保留，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">对</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">该等信息负有保密的义务，除根据相关法律法规、本协议的相关约定、或出于为用户提供更好的信用付款服务之目的、需将用户信息进行对外提供的情形之外，未经用户允许，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">不得</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">擅自将用户信息披露或提供给</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">其他第三</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">方。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">10</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">根据</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">信用付款服务平台管理制度、风险管理规定、相关法律法规要求等，从用户的信用付款金额、收货地址、联系方式等方面进行综合判断后如认为用户存在交易异常、个人信息异常等情形时，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">可</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">中止或调整向用户提供信用付款服务；为保障用户的交易安全，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权要求用户提供相关材料或要求用户</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">配合</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">其他风控</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">措施供</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">核实</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">验证，如用户拒绝相应材料或拒绝</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">配合</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">的风控</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">措施，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">导致</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">无法</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">核实交易正常，则</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权对用户的该笔订单采取交易拦截等方式，并可中止、终止向用户提供信用付款服务。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">11</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、为了充分保护用户的账户安全，当用户</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">访问</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">网站及其相关网站或</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">使用</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">提供</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的服务时，系统会记录用户操作的相关信息，这些信息可帮助我们更好地识别用户的身份以及保护用户的账户安全，例如用户的账户在可疑操作环境下登录的，系统可能监控到账户存在风险，采取一些措施避免资金损失。同时，为了向用户提供更全面的安全服务，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">可</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">将前述相关信息提供给</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">关联</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">公司和</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">集团</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">旗下公司。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第六条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">免责条款</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（一）</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">及</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">与提供信用付款服务相关平台的信息系统出现下列任</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">一</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">状况而无法正常运作，致使无法向用户提供本协议项下的各项服务，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">不</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">承担任何违约或赔偿责任，该状况包括但不限于：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、在服务网站维护期间；</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、电信设备出现故障不能进行数据传输的；</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、因台风、地震、海啸、洪水、停电、战争、恐怖袭击等不可抗力之因素，造成系统障碍不能执行业务的；</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、由于黑客攻击、电信部门和其他</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">信息技术依赖的相关部门、企事业单位技术调整或故障、网站升级、银行方面的问题等原因而造成的服务中断或者延迟。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（二）本协议有效期内，因国家相关主管部门颁布、变更的法令、政策</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">导致</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">或提供信用付款服务相关平台不能提供约定服务的，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">不</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">视为其违约，各方可根据相关的法令、政策变更协议内容或提前终止本协议，在此情况下，用户已经使用信用付款服务而尚未到期或偿还的任何款项（包括服务费和其他费用），视为立即到期，用户应立即归还，否则</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">仍</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有权按照本协议的约定采取合理的救济措施。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第七条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">协议变更、解除、终止和权利义务的转让</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（一）协议变更与解除</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权随时单方面修改本协议中与用户之间相关的权利义务，并及时以公告的方式通知用户。若用户不同意修改本协议，则应当立即停止使用信用付款服务并全额支</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">付本</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">协议项下全部应付款项，包括但不限于消费本金、分期服务费、违约金等；否则，视为用户同意并接受修改后的协议。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、经修订的协议一经通知，立即自动生效。一旦用户继续使用信用付款服务即被视为用户已接受了修改后的协议内容；如用户不同意相关变更，应自前述通知发出之日起停止使用服务并在</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">要求</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的期限内支付全部应付款项，包括但不限于消费本金、分期服务费、违约金等。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、本协议生效后，除本协议另有约定外，用户不得要求单方擅自变更或解除本协议。</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权基于自身经营考虑，因任何理由随时宣布中断、终止本协议或其任何部分，并要求用户在指定期限内支</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">付本</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">协议项下全部应付款项，包括但不限于消费本金、分期服务费、违约金等。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">（二）用户在使用信用付款服务的过程中，如果有下列情形发生，用户同意</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">权终止提供服务，用户应立即支付所有到期和未到期的应付款项，包括但不限于消费本金、分期服务费、违约金等：</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">1</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、用户主动关闭信用付款服务。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">2</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、用户个人</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">账户</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">被注销。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">3</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、冒用他人名义、盗用他人账户使用信用付款服务。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">4</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">、用户违反本协议约定导致本协议第四条约定的违约情形出现的。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">5</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、从事司法机构、监管机构等认为违法违规的消费行为，或信用付款服务提供方认定的不适当消费行为。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">6</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">、除上述原因外，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">有</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">权根据风险及自身业务运营情况需要随时中止（终止）向用户提供信用付款服务，因此导致用户无法使用服务或服务受到限制的，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">不</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">视为信用付款服务提供方违约，在此情况下，用户已经使用信用付款服务而尚未到期或偿还的任何款项（包括服务费和其他费用），视为立即到期，用户应立即归还。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（三）协议权利义务的转让未经信用付款服务提供方书面同意，用户不得将本协议项下的权利和义务转让给任何第三方。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">第八条</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">附则</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">（一）因本协议引起的或与本协议有关的争议，</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">可</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">与</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">会员</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">协商解决。协商不成的，任何一方均有权提起诉讼，并以</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">住所</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">地有管辖权的人民法院作为解决争议的管辖法院。</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; line-height:18.75pt; margin:0pt 0pt 3.75pt"><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">（二）本协议未尽事宜，以相关法律法规及《</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">用户注册协议》、《</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">白条服务费用计算规则》、《</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">自营商品售后服务政策》、《第三方卖家自主售后服务政策》</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">住</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">建鸟</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">委托</span><span style="color:#494949; font-family:宋体; font-size:10pt">的第三方公司的相关服务协议及其他平台规则约定为准</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div><div class="cnzz" style="display: none;">
  </div>

   
    </div>
</template>
<script>
    import api from '../../services/api'
    import core from '../../core/jsbridge/core'
    import error from '../../services/error'

    var store = {};
    var method = {};
    store.agree = '';

    method.getAgreement = function () {
      api.argremment({worker_id:store.worker_id}).then(function (res) {
        if (res.code == error.success){
          store.agree = res.result;
        }
      })
    };


  export default {
      name :"argremment",
      data () {
          return store;
      },
      methods:method,
      mounted () {
        //设置apptitle的方法
        store.title_info = {
          "title":"协议详情",
          "actionRight":{
            "actionIcon":"",
            "actionText":"",
            "actionTextColor":"#333333"//ios不传可能闪退
          },
          "bgColor":"#ffffff"
        };
        let hander = setInterval(function() {
          if(!window.WebViewJavascriptBridge) {
            return
          }
          else {
            clearInterval(hander)
          }
          try {
            core.$app('get_user_info','useInfo').then(function (res) {
              store.worker_info = JSON.parse(res);
              store.worker_id = store.worker_info.user_id;

              method.getAgreement();
            });
          }catch (e) {
            // console.log(e)
          }

          core.$app('title_info_control',store.title_info).then(function (res) {
          });

        },10);


        store.vm = this;
      }
  }
</script>
